May is handmade to order, each model is unique and will differ slightly from the picture shown

name: Mini Lucius
description:
Mini Lucius is a mini wired version of the original fox Lucius.

About 23 cm high (9"), made from cotton and linen,
recycled wool and polyester filling.
Mini Lucius wears shorts and a little scarf, his features are embroidered.

Mini Lucius can sit on its own or stand up against a wall.
Due to its delicate handmade nature it is not advised to use it
as a toy but rather as a nice companion to decorate a room.

Please note as it is handmade each mini Lucius is unique and 
will differ slightly from the pictures shown

Please order by MONDAY 2 DECEMBER for Christmas deliveries.

name: Printed Babette/ Collaboration with Hanna Konola
description:
A collaboration with Finnish designer Hanna Konola

I love Hanna's playful work and am delighted to have
worked with her on our Spring printed Babette series

The printed Babette is a new take on the original Babette doll
It is printed on a linen and cotton fabric 
filled with polyester filling
It measures about 9,5" or 24cm

Handwash with phosphate free detergent only
Please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery
sent via Royal mail recorded delivery

check Hanna's work on her website www.hannakonola.com
